item.title: CVE-2023-33986|2024-08-02T15:54:14.200Z -- sap_se -- sap%20crm%20abap%20%28grantor%20management%29
item.description: SAP CRM ABAP (Grantor Management) - versions 700, 701, 702, 712, 713, 714, does not sufficiently encode user-controlled inputs, resulting in Cross-Site Scripting (XSS) vulnerability. After successful exploitation, an attacker can cause limited impact on confidentiality and integrity of the application.
